Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:08.86,ED vi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}chiếu sáng lên anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:14.86,ED vi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}Hãy chiếu sáng cuộc đời sắp lụi tàn này.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.43,0:22:20.29,ED vi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}Chỉ muốn em tỏa sáng,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:23.60,ED vi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}chiếu sáng lên anh.
